<p>
 <strong> Who We Are: </strong>  Your portal to the most outrageous, adventerous, worldwide, 7-day vacations you've never had to plan!  If you've ever had 7 days to burn and became overwhelmed by the thought of who/what/where/when/why/how you are suppsoed to plan your vacation....we are your one-stop shop solution.
 </p>

<p>
<strong> What you will find on our site: </strong> A never ending list of pre-built itineraries which were excruciatingly planned, and then awesomely traveled yearly by 800+ of the most exclusive business school travelers in the country: Kellogg MBA students.  Each trip includes a high-level budget, a list of providers for each activity and is ranked by level of: <li> Culture/sightseeing </li> <li>Nightlife </li> <li> Physical Exertion</li> <li> Accomodations</li> <li> Free Time </li>
</p>

 <p>
 <strong> How you should navigate: </strong>  Start by identifying what continent you'd like to travel.  You will then see a list of countries with itineraries to suit your needs.  Each country has a list of multiple trips, which you can then sort through to view specific 7-day itineraries and a list of contacts to start booking!  So sit back, relax and enjoy perusing some of the best trips your brain could possibly imagine, all without spending a minute researching each location.
 </p>




